

🔄 Terraform Lifecycle
The lifecycle block gives fine-grained control over how resources behave. For example:

prevent_destroy: Avoids accidental resource deletion

create_before_destroy: Ensures zero downtime

ignore_changes: Prevents unnecessary changes from triggering updates

🔐 This is helpful for managing critical resources safely.


========================================================================================

resource "aws_s3_bucket" "example" {
  bucket = "my-secure-bucket"
  acl    = "private"

  lifecycle {
    prevent_destroy = true
    ignore_changes = [
      tags,
    ]
  }

  tags = {
    Name        = "TerraformBucket"
    Environment = "Dev"
  }
}
